-# Demo-only override of the engine's top-level layout (CafeCar ships the same
-# skeleton in app/views/layouts/application.html.haml). It exists solely to
-# inject the PostHog analytics snippet into <head> on the live demo. The
-# engine's _head / _body partials still resolve and render unchanged, so the
-# override adds tracking without forking the layout's behavior.
!!!
%html{lang: I18n.locale}
  %head
    = render "head"
    - if Rails.env.production?
      = render "layouts/posthog"
  %body{class: body_classes}= render "body"
